        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This *+1 resilient fire-resistant niyah\u00e1at* is often created to mark the passage of an Erutaki warrior into adulthood, plates salvaged from the exploded remains of a firewyrm elemental, with larger pieces protecting the chest, shoulders, and head. As you fight, the armor glows red hot.",
